Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.17,0:22:49.43,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}就决定不再哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:54.98,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur2}即使承担再多的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.98,0:23:00.11,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}仍有无法原谅的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.56,0:23:03.53,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已经无法回到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.53,0:23:06.03,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那平凡的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.03,0:23:11.12,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我还没有做成任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.12,0:23:16.37,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的记忆之碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.37,0:23:22.25,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}又有一块  消逝而去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:25.26,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回望今日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.26,0:23:28.01,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想变得更坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.01,0:23:33.14,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}期望这个声音总有一天可以传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.14,0:23:35.52,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.52,0:23:38.23,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在风停止的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.23,0:23:42.94,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}仰望天空追寻着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.69,0:23:50.28,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}在黎明前散发的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.45,0:23:55.83,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}将会变成彩虹
